yTime":"2019-09-02T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cc38ca1a42bcce80cb0c14d617e6b52edb5bec","tid":1530941,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"92f5af1cfab7f1e15d203a8f3dbbce4370f645d9","tid":1530941,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2X5W8mM_Wek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2X5W8mM_Wek&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=6d46af06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2X5W8mM_Wek</a>"},{"pid":"48d3f55ad9badf0cc30cabc04f609c4bce2ea1b0","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92f5af1cfab7f1e15d203a8f3dbbce4370f645d9","tid":1530941,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2X5W8mM_Wek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2X5W8mM_Wek&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=6d46af06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2X5W8mM_Wek</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3267d5bcdba54dd3300bf4b5d844750b96346b23","tid":1530941,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"48caa3c6efdf2407253c172069f0030812cde133","tid":1530941,"uid":223765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"香港人無路可退"},{"pid":"bfb7a28727d9025c9eb81dbf0e6d87746a268f05","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"今晚九巴可見又進一步"},{"pid":"fac83d4fff818de1d0cdeeee1ca5c466d738aa3e","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到最後的階級，警察會很輕易取得授權，只要任何嫌疑。即可侵入任何人的居所，進行搜查甚至破壞居住環境。這些嫌疑往往是警察主觀認定，不需要有任何客觀的犯罪證據。雖然法庭最後很可能都判當事人無罪。但警權已足夠對當事人進行足夠的滋擾，甚至有相當的未審先拘禁權力，加上多重標準，滋擾的對象也會集中在少數「麻煩份子」。也就是當靠行政手段已足夠恐嚇鎮壓所有反抗者。<br />\n<br />\n這樣，警察的權力基本上已慢慢架空法庭。因為警察有權不斷滋擾不喜歡的人，同時對於自己一方政治立場者，就予以放水。那樣，整個警察都已經陷入白色恐怖中。大家心裡都明白，只要抱持某些政治立場。警察就會上門找麻煩，相反另一個立場則不會出事。這樣，警察國家就完成了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去到最後階段喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20f1aaa148591bf1145e1536e83ec4077f83505","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"救港"},{"pid":"15010b3dc1d5fb0093491b2a428df3883bc14cc9","tid":1530941,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1acf567edd86e58a2946023cd38e9f6aea7f0a","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"10.1係死線<br />\n<br />\n之後共產黨一定發功，立新法就玩完"},{"pid":"564ab5442a7e46ebe748fa739f8e64c721672d2f","tid":1530941,"uid":168509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc513095d0c4be7a3bc0cacaa91261df1030e5d8","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"保皇正在推緊最後一步，叫林鄭用緊急法<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>完成了警察國家後，國家就可以不斷的通過新的法律。一些深刻的，定義含糊的法律。只要他願意解釋，每人都會觸犯的法律。使每人每天都在犯法，舉個例子，喝水是犯法。但是執法的嚴寬，卻由執法機關憑喜好去執行。平時服從的人，會被「法律不外乎人情」地開恩。「隻眼開隻眼閉」，有法不執被視為有人情味的表現。對於「麻煩份子」，則把法律看成最嚴刻。每天都可以因為他&quot;犯法&quot;而持續用行政手段玩弄。(其實依那些法律的標準，沒有人不犯法) 不僅法治完全崩潰，而法律本身的信用也完全崩潰。因為大家都知道，重點並不在於你是否有犯法。而是你跟政府的關係如何，關於好你犯法也會視而不見。關係不好，你生存就是犯法。社會走向完全的人治。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190923/s00001/1569240696895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190923%2Fs00001%2F1569240696895&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=9fbc531b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190923%2Fs00001%2F1569240696895&h=0edf2a18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190923/s00001/1569240696895</a><br />\n何君堯倡政府用《緊急法》 禁蒙面辱警<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190923/s00001/ac5cfd2c09c76c36c5dc9e6189f24fc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190923%2Fs00001%2Fac5cfd2c09c76c36c5dc9e6189f24fc9.jpg&h=54932f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會議員何君堯下午召開記者會，建議政府引用《緊急法》，處理近期示威和衝突，包括立法禁止蒙面和辱罵警員。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯提倡引用《緊急法》，在緊急情況下特首應考慮立蒙面法、辱警罪、防止記者阻礙警員執法、防止暴徒使用「光復香港，時代革命」一類港獨標語等。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，政府將在周四（26日）展開社區對話，惟不能一廂情願認為可令社會回復理智。"},{"pid":"41abea5e12bf802a1e1e7046dd5aca293d5e550d","tid":1530941,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b92a453cb23e6e4e1241caca662345b2f8f909","tid":1530941,"uid":247227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}